name: MusicalInstrumentsQuiz
0:
”Alexa open musical instruments quiz.”
”Alexa launch musical instruments quiz.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: musical instruments quiz
des:
Have Alexa quiz you on the sounds of musical instruments!

Alexa will play a sound and you will have to tell her which musical instrument played it. If you do not know an answer, you can say, "I give up." At any time, you can say, "Stop," and Alexa will tell you how you did on the quiz. Otherwise she will go through all 30 musical instrument sounds included in the quiz. Can you get them all correct?

To launch, simply say, "Alexa, open Musical Instruments Quiz."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
